 GPA - Truck Parts E-commerce Website

This project is a modern e-commerce web application for selling truck parts
It was built as part of my learning journey in web development using Next.js and React

 Features:
-  Shopping cart with quantity management
-  Product filtering (category, price, stock)
-  Stock status (In stock / Out of stock)

used:
- Next.js
- React
- Tailwind CSS


